headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires BMR Insurance
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Tustin, California-based Murray Gardner Insurance Agency Inc., dba BMR Insurance. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
